title: Live at LA RIOT Festival
description: LIVE FROM LOS ANGELES! An amazing live episode with amazing live guests JOE MANDE, CHRIS THAYER, JACQUELINE NOVAK, HARRIS WITTELS and JAMES ADOMIAN. Guys. It's weird, it's fun, it's funny, it's silly, it's brought to you by Pristique (not really). PLEASE ENJOY you weirdos!!
